&lt;Noranda Inc> said the company planned apublic share offer within three months of its Noranda ForestInc unit, which holds Noranda's forest products interests.    Size of the offer is still undetermined, Noranda said.    Noranda said Noranda Forest would operate as a freestandingsubsidiary of Noranda. Noranda Forest holds 100 pct of FraserInc, James Maclaren Industries and Noranda Forest Sales and 50pct stakes in MacMillan Bloedel Ltd &lt;MMBLF> and Northwood Pulpand Timber.     Noranda Forest's consolidated 1986 revenues were more thanthree billion dlrs, with earnings of 158 mln dlrs.&#3;